FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-base
WORKDIR /app
COPY frontend/package*.json ./
RUN npm ci
COPY frontend/ ./

FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-build
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=frontend-base /app ./
RUN npm run build

FROM nginx:alpine AS frontend
COPY --from=frontend-build /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html
COPY frontend/nginx.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf

CMD ["nginx", "-g", "daemon off;"]

FROM golang:1.21-alpine AS api-base
WORKDIR /app
COPY api/go.mod api/go.sum ./
RUN go mod download
COPY api/ ./

FROM golang:1.21-alpine AS api-build
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=api-base /app ./
RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -ldflags="-w -s" -o /server .

FROM alpine:3.19 AS api
COPY --from=api-build /server /server
EXPOSE 8080
CMD ["/server"]

FROM python:3.12-alpine AS worker-base
WORKDIR /app
COPY worker/requirements.txt ./
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
COPY worker/ ./

FROM python:3.12-alpine AS worker
WORKDIR /app
COPY --from=worker-base /usr/local/lib/python3.12/site-packages /usr/local/lib/python3.12/site-packages
COPY --from=worker-base /app ./
CMD ["celery", "-A", "tasks", "worker", "--loglevel=info"]
